<D>__{i've been going to aa and trying to be sober and this is what it got me.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{fired, for telling the truth.}
<A>__{mr. davies awkwardly puts his arm around kate's shoulder.}
<C>__{mr. davies}
<D>__{i'm sorry. i wish there was something i could do.}
